caption: Apply / Cancel
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/console
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/console/apply-cancel
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

''Apply'' walks the staged rows, executes each row's chosen action against
the wiki, then clears the staged and decision tiddlers.  ''Cancel'' clears
them without writing anything.

If any rename row has an invalid target title (empty, or matching an
existing tiddler), ''Apply'' is disabled and a red message points to the
offender.
